        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 7–8. Holotype of Teratozephyrus hinomaru from Fujioka (1994). 7, male adult, a=upperside; b=underside; 8, male genitalia. a=uncus and socii in dorsal view; b=genitalia capsule in right lateral view with valvae and aedeagus removed; c=valvae in right lateral view; d=phallus in right lateral view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4711144/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4711142>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 5–6. Male genitalia of Teratozephyrus spp. 5, T. yaolihuoi sp. nov., holotype, dissection number JF200; 6, T. hinomaru, dissection number TSY001. a=genitalia capsule with aedeagus removed, in left lateral view; b= ditto, in right lateral view; c= ditto, in ventral view; d=ditto, in dorsal view; e=valvae and juxta, in ventral view; f=ditto, in dorsal view; g= ditto, in ventroposterior view; h=right branch of gnathos (falx), in lateral view; i= ditto, in dorsal view; j=phallus in dorsal view; k=phallus in lateral view, in pale background, showing the sclerotized parts; l= ditto, in grey background, showing the membranous parts. LP=lateral process; LW=lateral window; jx=juxta. Scale=1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4711142/files/figure.png" .

